        "TileImage": "$($repository d6a3b494-28b8-40f7-a95b-bee0edebf384).Image",
        "Description": "Have you ever looked at a Hitman NPC and thought: &quot;Man, how I would massacre you if only you weren&apos;t a non target...&quot;? Well then you&apos;ve come to the right place pal! In this contract series I will pick out the most infuriating NPCs in every mission so that you can kill them without regret :)\r\rThe Stock Market is an absolute cluster of annoying enforcers. And I won&apos;t mention how many times I&apos;ve been spotted by Matteo on the stairs",
